docs.abstract: Relatively small, but significant, number of migrants fleeing crisis in Africa and Middle East are choosing northern route to better life by traveling through Russia and biking into Norway; refugees note that it is cheaper and safer than crossing by water, but long and cold path to crossing north of Arctic Circle.
